### MRI Axial Wrist (image 1 of 3)


The following three labled images show T2-weighted axial MRIs of the wrist. 
Image 1 is the most proximal and image 3 the most distal. 
The first image was taken at the distal forearm (radiograph on left shows the approximate location).  
